{"tid":547584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰機急折返 目擊者︰引擎爆咗下","createTime":"2018-02-01T14:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T15:01:33.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"111e4f20508ed8af9056121b5d67af773b67dabf","tid":547584,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T14:39:11.000Z","msg":"國泰客機疑引擎故障爆炸！一部離港客機國泰航空CX913，原定於晚上8時05分起飛往馬尼拉，飛行其間懷疑因為左邊引擎發生故障，須緊急折返香港赤鱲角機場。據目擊者於fb「香港航空討論區」發文稱，於往機場1號停車場取車期間，看見飛機的引擎爆炸，「佢爆嗰吓我望上去有火光，嗰吓係好震撼」，他又稱：「唔知撞雀定咩，爆一下之後不停有節奏咁小爆炸。」<br />\n目前消防已接報趕往機場，並派出至少5部救護車戒備。《蘋果》就事件向國泰查詢，國泰發言人指正了解事件。<br />\nCX913起飛後不久懷疑一度發生爆炸，據「flightradar24」網頁顯示，客機於晚上9時起飛，其後繼續攀升至近5千呎高度，於空中盤旋近半小時，其後折返香港機場，至晚上9時57分成功降落。<br />\n機場管理局發言人回應《蘋果》稱，機管局於晚上9時10分，收到機場控制塔通知，一班前往馬尼拉的國泰航空航機CX913，需要緊急折返及要求戒備。該航機其後於晚上時分安全降落，機場運作無受影響。至於肇事原因，機管局指需要向國泰查詢。<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/547565/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/547565/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6d6795e014fc2bdb798d51990dc45e2c581699d7","tid":547584,"uid":60686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T14:40:46.000Z","msg":"仲諗住係東方報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956f279300e5eb0df6de32301481ec5725726671","tid":547584,"uid":73412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d6795e014fc2bdb798d51990dc45e2c581699d7","tid":547584,"uid":60686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T14:40:46.000Z","msg":"仲諗住係東方報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T14:43:45.000Z","msg":"呢d真正大單野就梗係周圍都有報"},{"pid":"e372fa0147f0ee46468dc93d3fe7fabdadfa7d69","tid":547584,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T14:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b7965ff858afe3587d7ec9fe9a8742705df252","tid":547584,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T14:57:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180201/57782477\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180201%2F57782477&d=8SIJ3bEWRS%2FHeheCzVHYaAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=54dc0f6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180201%2F57782477&h=fd005e2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180201/57782477</a>"},{"pid":"704d1edff848b322e896dec0747e14f6afd96156","tid":547584,"uid":66246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T15:01:12.000Z","msg":"heaco班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a6c629d98f84f10f8bdee0bcc6d25353e0a173","tid":547584,"uid":1435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"引擎爆左 右邊冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}